WEBVTT

00:19.164 --> 00:20.096
Dang!

00:20.196 --> 00:22.294
Hooked it.

00:22.394 --> 00:25.924
Dude sure doesn't look much
like his head shot anymore.

00:26.024 --> 00:28.056
That's what 20-some years
of the bottle looks like.

00:28.156 --> 00:29.854
Must've been some
hard-ass years.

00:29.954 --> 00:32.052
Sure this isn't
a waste of time?

00:32.152 --> 00:33.583
You like driving balls.

00:33.684 --> 00:36.014
10 bucks, hit him.
Three swings.

00:36.114 --> 00:37.247
You're on.

00:38.579 --> 00:40.344
But you know
what I'm saying.

00:40.444 --> 00:42.076
Waits confessed.

00:42.176 --> 00:45.073
Why you always got to look
a gift horse in the mouth?

00:45.173 --> 00:47.171
Arthur delacroix endured
prolonged abuse,

00:47.271 --> 00:48.637
then goes missing?

00:48.737 --> 00:50.401
Father tells the daughter
he reported it,

00:50.501 --> 00:51.700
but doesn't.

00:51.800 --> 00:54.297
That puts Sam delacroix
out there,

00:54.397 --> 00:55.797
prime suspect.

00:55.896 --> 00:57.762
Unless somebody else
confesses.

00:57.862 --> 00:59.459
We always
get false confessions.

00:59.559 --> 01:00.792
Waits is a psychopath.

01:00.892 --> 01:02.624
How'd he know
about the starfish?

01:04.455 --> 01:06.187
I'm just saying.

01:09.517 --> 01:11.749
Nice shot, tiger.

01:11.849 --> 01:14.079
I get to be tiger
'cause I'm black?

01:14.179 --> 01:16.344
Because you're good.

01:16.444 --> 01:18.610
No cigar, but you're
pissing him off.

01:18.643 --> 01:20.041
You think it's so easy,
you try it.

01:20.141 --> 01:21.173
I don't golf.

01:21.273 --> 01:22.239
Golf is a great sport.

01:22.339 --> 01:24.070
Golf is not a great sport.

01:24.170 --> 01:25.603
If you can smoke and drink
while you're doing it,

01:25.669 --> 01:26.735
it's not a sport.

01:26.835 --> 01:28.700
Well, it might relax you.

01:28.800 --> 01:30.699
Lord knows you need it.

01:30.798 --> 01:33.596
There's more to life
than work.

01:33.662 --> 01:35.194
Get your wallet out,
Harry.

01:41.221 --> 01:43.419
[ Clang ]

01:43.587 --> 01:44.586
That's what
I'm talking about!

01:44.686 --> 01:46.717
[ Laughs ]
Ooh.

01:55.441 --> 01:57.840
[ Laughs ]

01:57.939 --> 01:59.605
Now that we got his attention,
we gonna go talk to him or what?

01:59.705 --> 02:03.168
No, we go to palm Springs,
talk to the mother,

02:03.268 --> 02:05.866
get some background,
brace pops.

02:05.966 --> 02:08.264
Let's go.
Aren't we forgetting
something, partner?

02:12.326 --> 02:14.124
See, don't be like that.

02:14.224 --> 02:16.222
I hate to lose.

